# Generated / build artifacts, committed on purpose — the Svelte SPA is embedded
# into the Go binary via //go:embed (so `go build`/`go install` work without a Node
# toolchain), and api-types.ts is generated from the Go wire contract by tygo.
# Marking them keeps the churn out of code review:
#   linguist-generated=true → GitHub collapses them in PR diffs + drops them from
#                             the repo's language stats.
#   -diff                   → git skips textual diffs for the minified bundle
#                             (still reported as changed, so CI's freshness check
#                             and `git diff --quiet` keep working).

# Embedded, pre-built web bundle (regenerate with `make web-build`).
internal/web/frontend/dist/** linguist-generated=true -diff

# Generated TypeScript types mirrored from Go apitypes (regenerate with `make web-types`).
internal/web/frontend/src/lib/api-types.ts linguist-generated=true
